snippet.textDisplay:
Neopets is amazing. Do not shit on neopets. I've played it for at least 14 years (since I was somewhere between 7 and 10), and it's the best. I could never get above 100k neopoints, because I was an impulsive kid who spent everything on anything. I had a plushie collection. It was great. I'm now 23 years old, and I only just learned to use the Stock Market (when I was in university, very bored, 'working on' an assignment). Neopets is amazing. There's nothing like building up your shop on the first weekend of every month. Tell Amanda that. You get mad stocks. It's great. I met my girlfriend over 10 years ago and even now, to this day, we play neopets together. My stocks are intense, but underwhelming. This game has got me addicted to Kou-Jong. I play it three times a day, every day. Neopets is amazing. I would give my life for neopets. Did you know it was once associated with Scientology? That was great. Good times. It also had a PS2 game. Also good times.
Anyway. Neopets. Good, yes? Very good. My username is 'Charlockle' at current, my username used to be 'charlotte8872488', and before that... who knows? I can't remember. I forgot the password because I was under the age of 7, and my first account was lost to the sands of time. Now here I stand, a 23 year old man, playing neopets still to this day.
I only just hit 3 mill neopoints. It's been 14 years.
